dmca.title: Froogle DMCA complaint - Net Enforcer35 - Universal Remote
dmca.body:
complaints

I, the undersigned, CERTIFY UNDER PENALTY OF PERJURY that I am an agent
authorized to act on behalf of the owner of certain intellectual
property rights, said owner being named [Universal Remote] ("IP Owner").
I have a good faith belief that the listings or materials listed below
are not authorized by the above IP Owner, its agent, or the law and
therefore infringe the IP Owner's rights according to state, federal, or
United States law. Please act expeditiously to remove or disable access
to the material or items claimed to be infringing.

Identity of advertisement(s) at issue/Images owned by [Universal
Remote]/:

Wholesale Connection

http://froogle.google.com/froogle_image?q=http://www.wholesaleconnection.com/site/media/images/8969.jpg&size=2&dhm=3c7cd00c&hl=en
